  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">KPMG - FH Internal Audit</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SV">KPMG - FH Internal Audit</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="SV">Revisionen ska genomf&#xF6;ras f&#xF6;r att s&#xE4;kerst&#xE4;lla att mediefonden f&#xF6;r Demokratiska republiken Kongo (DRK) har hanterats i enlighet med det s&#xE4;rskilda avtalet mellan Sverige och Fondation Hirondelle-kontoret i Demokratiska republiken Kongo (10853).
Dessutom omfattar detta uppdrag bed&#xF6;mning av intern styrning och kontroll av Fondation Hirondelle och att identifiera eventuella svagheter. Baserat p&#xE5; resultaten kommer ambassaden att kr&#xE4;va att Fondation Hirondelle (nedan kallad &quot;organisationen&quot;) behandlar svagheterna antingen f&#xF6;re eller under avtalsperioden. N&#xE5;gra av &#xE5;tg&#xE4;rderna kommer att ing&#xE5; som avtalsvillkor som ska f&#xF6;ljas upp under den &#xE5;rliga revisionen.</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The audits shall be carried out to ensure that Media funds for the Democratic Republic of Congo (DRC) have been handled in accordance with the Special Agreement between Sweden and the Fondation Hirondelle office in DRC (10853).

In addition, this assignment includes assessment on the internal management and control of Fondation Hirondelle. To identify eventual weaknesses. Based on the findings, the embassy will require that Fondation Hirondelle (hereafter called the &#x201C;organization&#x201D;) addresses the weaknesses as appropriate before or during the agreement phase. Some of the measures will be included as agreement conditions to be followed up during the annual audit.</narrative>
  </description>
